snippet.title: J-Stars Victory Vs+ (PS4) - Goku vs Naruto Gameplay [1080p] TRUE-HD QUALITY
snippet.description:
►► Remember to select 720p or 1080p HD◄◄
Goku vs Naruto gameplay in the Playstation 4 version of J-Stars Victory Vs+.

Characters in the game:

    Son Goku (Dragon Ball Z)
    Vegeta (Dragon Ball Z)
    Freeza (Dragon Ball Z)
    Naruto Uzumaki (Naruto Shippuden)
    Sasuke Uchiha (Naruto Shippuden)
    Madara Uchiha (Naruto Shippuden)
    Monkey D. Luffy (One Piece)
    Boa Hancock (One Piece)
    Akainu (One Piece)
    Portgas D. Ace (One Piece)
    Ichigo Kurosaki (Bleach)
    Sosuke Aizen (Bleach)
    Toriko (Toriko)
    Zebra (Toriko)
    Kenshin Himura (Rurouni Kenshin)
    Shishio Makoto (Rurouni Kenshin)
    Gintoki Sakata (Gintama)
    Kankichi Ryotsu (Kochikame)
    Gon Freecss (Hunter × Hunter)
    Killua Zoldyck (Hunter x Hunter)
    Hiei (Yu Yu Hakusho)
    Yusuke Urameshi (YuYu Hakusho)
    Younger Toguro (YuYu Hakusho)
    Taro Yamada (Chinyūki -Tarō to Yukaina Nakama-tachi-)
    Medaka Kurokami (Medaka Box)
    Tsunayoshi Sawada with Reborn (Reborn!)
    Tatsumi Oga with Beelzebub (Beelzebub)
    Jonathan Joestar (JoJo’s Bizarre Adventure)
    Joseph Joestar (JoJo’s Bizarre Adventure)
    Meisuke “Nuubee” Nueno (Jigoku Sensei Nube)
    Korosensei (Assassination Classroom)
    Pegasus Seiya (Saint Seiya)
    Kenshiro (Fist of the North Star)
    Raoh (Fist of the North Star)
    Arale (Dr. Slump)
    Bobobo-bo Bo-bobo (Bobobo-bo Bo-bobo)
    Kusuo Saiki (Saiki Kusuo no Psi Nan)
    Luckyman (Tottemo Luckyman)
    Momotaro Tsurugi (Sakigake!! Otokojuku)

J-Stars Victory VS Support Characters

These characters are not playable, but can be called upon the player to help during battle by pressing the L2 button on the J-Stars Victory VS Controls. It’s worth noting playable characters can be used as support, but the list below is of characters that can only function as support.

    Jaguar Junichi (Pyu to Fuku! Jaguar)
    Misogi Kumagawa (Medaka Box)
    Rukia Kuchiki (Bleach)
    Lala Satalin Deviluke (To-LOVE-ru)
    Chitoge Kirisaki (Nisekoi)
    Kagura with Sadaharu (Gintama)
    Tetsuya Kuroko (Kuroko’s Basketball)
    Yusuke Fujisaki, Hime Onizuka, Kazuyoshi Usui (Sket Dance)
    Neuro Nogami (Neuro: Supernatural Detective)
    Allen Walker (D.Gray-man)
    Hisoka (Hunter x Hunter)
    Hinata Shoyo (Haikyu!!)
    Heihachi Edajima (Sakigake!! Otokojuku)


Platforms: Playstation 4, PS3 & PS Vita
Publisher: Namco Bandai
Developer: Ban Dai
Genre: Fighting
Release Date:
US: June 30, 2015
EU: June 25, 2015
